data.title: B Tiles to Mid Courtyard Leer
data.description: This is a good leer to blind anyone peaking B Tiles from Mid or Mid Catwalk. This is perfect to peak an oper peaking you from A Tree.

data.title: A Main to A Site Leer
data.description: This is a good leer to blind A Site from A Main allowing your team to execute and take the site.

data.title: A Lobby to A Main Leer
data.description: This is a good leer to blind your enemies peaking A Main allowing you to push and take control and clear angles.

data.title: Mid Courtyard to Mid Bottom Leer
data.description: This is a good leer to push Mid and clear close angles along with blinding anyone peaking from B Market.

data.title: B Main to B Site Leer
data.description: This is a good leer to push into B Site and clear angles towards B Switch.

data.title: B Lobby to B Main Leer
data.description: This is a good leer to help your team push into B Main from B Lobby.
